longBusinessSummary: H3Enterprises, Inc. owns, creates, licenses, franchises, and operates HipHopSodaShops in the United States. Its HipHopSodaShops provide food, merchandising, memorabilia, recording studio, liquid crystal display screens, and video gaming facilities. The company also operates H3GameLine.com, an online gaming portal for cyber sports competition. H3Enterprises, Inc. is based in Boca Raton, Florida.
